These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, water
City: new-york, berlin, liverpool
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, cricket
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, analyst, fisherman
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, malaysian
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, airplane, tram
 1. the manager is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
 2. the australian is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
 4. the malaysian is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person driving the tram##7
 5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fisherman##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is not the british##6
 8. the australian is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the analyst is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person driving the tram is not the person who's sport is cricket##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | juice       | lemonade  | water     |
| City          | liverpool       | berlin  | new-york    |
| Sport         | skiing  | cricket   | skateboarding |
| Job   | manager | fisherman   | analyst     |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian | british   |
| Transport           | airplane  | bus      | tram  |

