The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, jazz, trance
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, scrabble
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, boat, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 3. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of trance is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person eating plum##7
 5. the gothic-revival house is not the person driving the trike##6
 6. the person eating papaya is between the person playing snooker and the fan of jazz##2
 7. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 8. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the person eating plum and the tower house##7
 9. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the cat is not the person playing snooker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3       |
| Food          | orange       | papaya         | plum         |
| House         | tower  | gothic-revival         | townhouse   |
