The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, rock
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, grey, brown
House: tower, modern, wooden
 1. the tower house is the person who likes brown##1
 2. the designer is the havana-smoker##1
 3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 4. the tower house is on the left of the designer##1
 5. the analyst is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the dannemann-smoker##7
 7. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
 8. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 9. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
10. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
11. the fan of dubstep is not the person watching time-travel movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3      |
| Cigar      | dannemann    | havana    | fonseca |
| Job         | analyst  | designer | videographer     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | time-travel | spy         |
