.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, sprite
3 different games are played: go, whist, poker
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, car, taxi
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, daisy
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, reading, woodworking
3 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, mouse
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsdaffodil##7
 5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 6. the person driving the car is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 7. the person driving the train is between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 9. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
10. the person playing go is not the person driving the car##6
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the train##1
12. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | cola      | hot-chocolate | sprite      |
| Game          | whist    | go          | poker |
| Transport           | car   | train    | taxi    |
| Flower   | daffodil | poppy       | daisy      |
| Hobby   | writing   | reading           | woodworking      |
| Pet           | mouse     | cat           | guinea-pig  |

