.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-19::.
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, scrabble
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, coach, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, western
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, rock, trance
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, fuchsia, yellow
3 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, hedgehog
 1. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
 2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 3. the scientist is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 4. the owner of the snake is the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the coach is on the right of the scientist##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
10. the person who likes yellow is the police-officer##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
12. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the fan of trance##7
13. the fan of rock is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Game      | snooker | chess         | scrabble  |
| Job         | scientist  | coach | police-officer  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | drama       | western |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | rock        | trance  |
| Color         | fuchsia    | ebony  | yellow    |
| Pet     | hedgehog      | goldfish   | snake    |

