.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, nurse, paramedic
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, april, october
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, dutch
House: ranch-style, craftsman, townhouse
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, reggae, country
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, white
 1. the accountant is not the fan of techno##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 3. the ranch-style house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the townhouse house##7
 4. the paramedic is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the fan of techno is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 6. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
 7. the fan of reggae is on the right of the accountant##1
 8. the american is the person who likes white##1
 9. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
10. the ranch-style house is the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Job           | paramedic    | accountant | nurse    |
| Birthday   | october       | april    | november   |
| Nationality   | dutch        | colombian  | american |
| House           | townhouse       | ranch-style   | craftsman     |
| Music-Genre         | techno | country | reggae |
| Color     | fuchsia       | lavender | white    |

 